{"tid":204930,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"這 9 個巨星的招牌 李安納度的「舉杯」畫面每個都超經典","createTime":"2017-04-17T12:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T12:11:49.000Z","uid":9573,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcaadd6c62d6c1dbecbc3b2e563698222d442312","tid":204930,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:01:14.000Z","msg":"喜歡看電影的大家，是不是有發現，有些演員的演出，好像似曾相似？每個演員除了有各自的演技路數外，也有自己的招牌動作，讓大家一看，有種「是你」的感覺！<br />\n<br />\n強尼戴普的帽子<br />\n你不能想像出傑克船長、威利萬卡或瘋帽子沒有帽子的樣子。然而，即使他不是一個童話角色，強尼戴普總是戴著帽子一個。而他的粉絲們也注意到他也在現實生活中也是個帽子控喲！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afe4df772.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afe4df772.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=a58f6adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afec121e6.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afec121e6.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=65a39187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1b0b490028.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1b0b490028.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=1cf5841a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山謬傑克森的傳道<br />\n山謬傑克森只是喜歡很慷慨激昂的講話。他的第一次這樣做是在《黑色追緝令》，從那以後，就繼續使用他的口才，他的粉迷們超愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afef2215c.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afef2215c.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=bfa903a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afe729635.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afe729635.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=4ee5e853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李奧納多迪卡皮歐的舉杯<br />\n沒有人比李奧納多迪卡皮歐更喜歡舉杯了。他在《鐵達尼號》中那個金髮帥哥的帥氣形象，不知道迷死了多少少女，之後，他《決殺令》、《華爾街之狼》，當然還有《大亨小傳》，每一幕真的都超經典的！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afe649118.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afe649118.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=bc3ff640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afefc694b.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afefc694b.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=ee8004e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湯姆克魯斯的衝刺<br />\n「跑得跟湯姆克魯斯一樣」（Running like Tom Cruise）已經變成美國的一句諺語。他演出的電影裡，真的都必須在屏幕上狂奔，你不得不承認，無論周圍環境如何，他都很擅長衝刺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1aff1375d5.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1aff1375d5.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=f80c531f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1aff074ea9.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1aff074ea9.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=d5f10761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哈里遜福特的死亡之指<br />\n哈里遜福特很喜歡用手指指著別人。他在幾乎每一部電影中都使用這個手勢，他的「死亡之指」第一次出現是在「星際大戰」系列中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afecd7452.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afecd7452.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=383c0ca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afee79ddb.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afee79ddb.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=45da2117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蜜雪兒羅德里奎茲的強悍形象<br />\n如果米蜜雪兒羅德里奎茲在一部電影中亮相，你可以確定她表現的會比所有的男性角色更好。她不僅一直重複同樣的姿，角色特質也類似，甚至穿著非常相似的服裝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afe5a0abc.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afe5a0abc.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=81651453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afeb28121.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afeb28121.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=ff467734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提姆羅斯的放鬆<br />\n這位英國演員演繹的無論是謊言專家還是摩納哥王子，他總會找到坐在舒適的沙發椅上放鬆的理由。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afea70fd2.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afea70fd2.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=b7f291ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afe9d2b60.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afe9d2b60.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=8b214846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梅爾吉布遜的裸體<br />\n梅爾吉布遜有一個好身材，他比其他男性演員更頻繁地表現出他的完全或部分赤裸的身體。梅爾也被認為是裸體場景的先驅，因為他在 1987 年在《致命武器》中開始裸體出現，謝謝梅叔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afe8a648c.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afe8a648c.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=c0935c6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱千雪毫不遮掩地吃<br />\n演員大多是活著的人，所以有時候他們必須在鏡頭前吃東西並不奇怪。但是畢彼特一直以來吃得有點過分，而且還很寫實，當我們看著他吃東西時，也會不知不覺癢癢跑到冰箱前覓食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/936Ha8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F936Ha8.png&h=a5ffbbd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XT3Fja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXT3Fja.png&h=8df2d74e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22ru55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22ru55.png&h=96b42e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8o3dn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8o3dn.png&h=5360d901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/019t00L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F019t00L.png&h=a6917474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afed89285.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afed89285.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=11af7626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64789/58f1afefc694b.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64789%2F58f1afefc694b.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=ee8004e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84395259bb4c1666a6c946a7a81cbcea949ee2a2","tid":204930,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b65ab71bbd53d12a6a957fd9ba0177e67cad154","tid":204930,"uid":53800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:03:33.000Z","msg":"最尾係巨星？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af17054279c76391b7712f81ab50571ed591616f","tid":204930,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:03:33.000Z","msg":"千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3fe3ad5b43470e7e5bd0151a44d4b30844f509","tid":204930,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"入嚟睇朱千雪"},{"pid":"2d591542d94496e0e0f47f2c52bfcdf9de7a77cd","tid":204930,"uid":28845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"正評俾千雪"}]}